{"tid":2402550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登新上任靜靜雞撤孔子學院限制令 被質疑放任中國間諜外宣","createTime":"2021-02-10T13:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T01:28:46.000Z","uid":63183,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"66a817f627c3549d0d73da0391b4f4fbdee35f65","tid":2402550,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfLG7ZV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfLG7ZV.png&h=6b034ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由中國資助、以推廣普通話為名而廣設各國嘅孔子學院，早前被指係中國政治宣傳機構，前美國國務卿蓬佩奧指斥係間諜機構，要求全面關閉。前美國總統特朗普更加以總統行政命令要求，由幼稚園以至大學都需要披露同孔子學院嘅合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n但呢項行政命令被揭發俾拜登靜靜雞咁取消咗。美國現任總統拜登喺冇任何公布嘅情況下取消咗呢項限制政策，最終係有傳媒查返美國資訊與監管事務辦公室（OIRA）嘅紀錄先發現，拜登喺1月26日已經靜靜雞取消咗呢項政策，當時佢只係上任唔夠一個禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n眾議員麥卡錫（Kevin McCarthy）都轉貼報導，批評拜登政府駡疫情蔓延一年之際，不但冇俾中共為咗顛倒是非嘅行為負責，反而仲獎勵中國，俾佢哋嘅政治宣傳滲透至大學校園。<br />\n<br />\n前美國總統特朗普之前指出，根據聯邦調查局（FBI）同美國司法部（DOJ）嘅調查，孔子學院以大量資金，偽裝成語言同文化活動，藉此進行可疑嘅活動。雖然孔子學院未曾全面公開同中國共產黨嘅聯繫，佢哋同中國政府嘅統戰機器同知識產權盜竊都有密切關連。"},{"pid":"25d4879968774607c6f35d7df8f13e71188bbbe3","tid":2402550,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a5bd7edf543b6cd72e2c6067a58ff90e89ed838","tid":2402550,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436707d72776113b97a55d80f3e799a30909f2bb","tid":2402550,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ebf2258ae96e93e54c266e8024d08ec5e989f8","tid":2402550,"uid":377064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"國際線班人識玩一定係向民主黨班議員施壓，而唔係鳩up話要拜登解釋"},{"pid":"714151833c0d2ebbb3c3a9452fff62217835bd0b","tid":2402550,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4862021dd546b65009fd2f903230314236c0c6","tid":2402550,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T00:50:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cd4eacb5cdf38a6a71169e656f9a6b9ef028863","tid":2402550,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1875e2762494b8631896e8fe00bd9315f0ff81e","tid":2402550,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:24:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">兩</span>"},{"pid":"f1d77d3a70eb7c133964112e6a64fd7ce03c5e0e","tid":2402550,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:24:36.000Z","msg":"兩黨共識既野  我地識條春"},{"pid":"63348890e874b1c906a5961d18487de6fb2da15f","tid":2402550,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f3ebf2258ae96e93e54c266e8024d08ec5e989f8","tid":2402550,"uid":377064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"國際線班人識玩一定係向民主黨班議員施壓，而唔係鳩up話要拜登解釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"你唔係美國人就唔好搞咁多野"},{"pid":"1667482e731d93d2b762bd0338d1b0c774108874","tid":2402550,"uid":173784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ccd4ec72a930a518113a8bb9d33917b00757979","tid":2402550,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021